WEBVTT

00:06.335 --> 00:07.307
You've got no choice.

00:07.332 --> 00:10.168
Of course, I do,
and I not to attend.

00:10.857 --> 00:11.601
Morning Baker.

00:11.626 --> 00:13.912
All due respect, you're being
incredibly unreasonable.

00:13.937 --> 00:15.492
Part of my gruff charm.

00:15.517 --> 00:16.898
The Citizens Defense League

00:16.923 --> 00:18.818
is a legitimate
civil-rights organization.

00:18.843 --> 00:22.120
In the eyes of the IRS,
for tax purposes maybe.

00:22.145 --> 00:25.095
Anyone else with half a brain,
sees them for what they are.

00:25.120 --> 00:27.723
A left-wing
political action cabal.

00:27.748 --> 00:30.068
They just want you to attend
their awards dinner next week.

00:30.409 --> 00:31.856
Dreams die hard.

00:31.881 --> 00:34.079
Forward the invitation
to the Inspector General.

00:34.104 --> 00:35.836
She's got a prior
engagement in D.C.

00:35.861 --> 00:37.856
Lucky her.
Still a pass.

00:37.881 --> 00:40.252
We've got the Police Academy
curriculum meeting at 10.

00:40.277 --> 00:40.844
Ok.

00:40.869 --> 00:43.848
Won't look right. A representative
from the NYPD should be there.

00:43.873 --> 00:45.912
You look smart in a tux.
Have a great evening.

00:45.937 --> 00:47.752
Look, I know
you don't like people...

00:47.777 --> 00:49.597
I don't like these people?

00:49.622 --> 00:52.808
The CDL is a bunch
of radical fringe bottom feeders,

00:52.833 --> 00:56.047
who raise money
by vilifying the NYPD.

00:58.086 --> 01:00.239
Final answer.
No!

01:04.617 --> 01:06.584
(sighs)

01:06.586 --> 01:08.770
(garbled radio transmission)

01:10.706 --> 01:12.374
(siren wailing in distance)

01:12.376 --> 01:14.209
Double check
that air vent.

01:14.211 --> 01:15.510
Right there.

01:15.512 --> 01:16.878
(dog barking)

01:16.880 --> 01:19.130
DANNY:
Ah, what a mess.

01:19.132 --> 01:21.182
Who'd be crazy enough
to bomb a mosque?

01:21.184 --> 01:22.634
Hey, Rick.

01:22.636 --> 01:23.852
How's it going?

01:23.854 --> 01:25.003
Could be worse. You?

01:25.005 --> 01:26.170
Ah, you know.

01:26.172 --> 01:28.940
Same old same old.
Maria Baez, Rick Kelly.

01:28.942 --> 01:30.725
Best marshal
the FDNY has,

01:30.727 --> 01:32.527
not to mention the best
third baseman

01:32.529 --> 01:34.279
the softball team's ever had.

01:34.281 --> 01:35.780
Yeah, not anymore. Bum knee.

01:35.782 --> 01:37.198
What have we got here?
Looks like

01:37.200 --> 01:38.650
a pipe bomb tossed
through a window.

01:38.652 --> 01:40.819
Pipe bomb. Anybody hurt?

01:40.821 --> 01:42.287
We got lucky.

01:42.289 --> 01:44.656
Smoke inhalation,
minor burns, but no casualties.

01:44.658 --> 01:46.741
How bad's the damage?

01:46.743 --> 01:48.410
The collateral fire
we put out pretty quick.

01:48.412 --> 01:50.161
We're still assessing
the structure.

01:50.163 --> 01:51.579
Hate crime task force
takes it from there.

01:51.581 --> 01:52.998
Thanks.

01:53.000 --> 01:54.749
You got it.
Good to meet you, Baez.

01:54.751 --> 01:56.968
You, too.

01:57.753 --> 01:59.087
He's married.

01:59.089 --> 02:00.255
Just browsing.

02:00.257 --> 02:01.423
Ah. Just telling you.

02:01.425 --> 02:02.640
MAN:
Detectives,

02:02.642 --> 02:04.876
this is Imam Ansar.

02:04.878 --> 02:06.895
Imam, were you here
when the bomb went off?

02:06.897 --> 02:09.547
I was leading prayers
when I heard the window break.

02:09.549 --> 02:11.433
Then there was
an explosion and fire.

02:11.435 --> 02:14.019
You have any idea who would
want to do this to a mosque?

02:14.021 --> 02:15.720
I thought that was your job.

02:15.722 --> 02:19.107
Well, it is our job, but you
live here and we don't.

02:19.109 --> 02:21.860
There are people who don't
want us in the neighborhood.

02:21.862 --> 02:24.079
So, you've had trouble before?

02:24.081 --> 02:25.229
Several break-ins.

02:25.231 --> 02:27.332
They write on the walls--
blame us for 9/11

02:27.334 --> 02:28.666
and everything else.

02:28.668 --> 02:30.668
They hate us
because they fear us.

02:30.670 --> 02:32.570
But our religion
celebrates peace.

02:32.572 --> 02:35.040
Those people only know
what they see on TV

02:35.042 --> 02:37.208
when it comes to your religion.

02:37.210 --> 02:38.343
Those few who do violence

02:38.345 --> 02:40.128
in the name of Allah
are not true Muslims,

02:40.130 --> 02:42.881
and they bring violence
upon those of us who are.

02:42.883 --> 02:46.017
And we are left unprotected.

02:46.019 --> 02:47.919
Feel the love?

02:47.921 --> 02:50.421
Well, rule number one
when I was in Fallujah:

02:50.423 --> 02:51.740
never trust Americans.

02:51.742 --> 02:54.526
Then why choose to live here
if that's how he feels?

02:54.528 --> 02:57.312
I don't know why they choose
to live here, but they do,

02:57.314 --> 02:59.280
and the sign on the door
says everyone's welcome,

02:59.282 --> 03:02.283
so we got to back
that up, partner.

